metadata.name: Embark the journey
metadata.description:
"Chapter one"

Her name is Scarlet Cla'ris, 30 yrs old. despite that age. she is born as a cat race and that age, it still consider youth age as if she is 17 years old. she is a young warrior who leaves her hometown to do her journey. ready to see the vast world.  what kind of adventure will she get along in her journey?
